OL,5,GWhat do viewers in Northern Ireland
OL,6,Gcall the third channel? ITV? ITV1? UTV?
OL,7,GThe UTV? Ulster Television?
OL,9,FThe name ITV plc thinks you should use
OL,10,Fis not at all clear even if the station
OL,11,Fbranding is now strong and explicit.
OL,13,FWith the revamp of ITV 1, visually
OL,14,FUTV's brand seems to have reached its
OL,15,Ffinal destination.
OL,17,FTrails now follow the standard ITV 1
OL,18,Fformat. 1s fly over the screen as the
OL,19,Ftrail transitions to the endboard. Then
OL,20,Fat the very end the ITV 1 logo wipes
OL,21,Fon.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
