OL,5,FUTV is effectively a hallmark  a
OL,6,Ftrusted brand which brings together the
OL,7,Flocal output.
OL,9,FVisually there is no doubt the channel
OL,10,Fname is ITV 1  trails, idents and the
OL,11,FDOG all highlight the name.
OL,13,FBefore it was just about conceivable
OL,14,Fthe ITV name (left out of local promos)
OL,15,Fwas just the old generic name for the
OL,16,Fnetwork.
OL,18,FBut orally the name is less clear.
OL,19,FAnnouncements before local programmes
OL,20,Frarely, if ever, give a name.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
OL,22,                                   G2/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
