OL,5,FBut trails still tend to end with the
OL,6,Fwords "on UTV"  even with the ITV 1
OL,7,Fname on screen.
OL,9,FSimilarly the EPG still refers solely
OL,10,Fto UTV.
OL,12,FITV has always been very hesitant to be
OL,13,Fseen as downgrading the UTV brand. It
OL,14,Fis, of course, a name which goes back
OL,15,Fmany years.
OL,17,FBut we're at the point where the
OL,18,Fremaining hesitancy seems hard to
OL,19,Fjustify.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
