OL,5,FEven if there was a reluctance to
OL,6,Fexplicitly voice the name "ITV 1" on a
OL,7,Flocal trail, there are ways round this.
OL,9,FThe UTV Life trail points the way.
OL,10,FSimply don't say UTV as the channel
OL,11,Fname. Use the brand in other ways.
OL,12,FPerhaps in the title of the programme?
OL,13,FPerhaps by including a more subtle use
OL,14,Fof the name: "Join the UTV news team
OL,15,Ffor View from Stormont, Monday at
OL,16,F10.45pm."
OL,18,FThe other mystery concerns the EPG
OL,19,Fname.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
