OL,5,FIn English regions the name is simply
OL,6,F"ITV 1". Wales and the Scottish part of
OL,7,Fthe Border region are afforded an
OL,8,Fappropriate suffix.
OL,10,FBut the EPG name in Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fremains UTV alone.
OL,13,FTake one step back. This risks being
OL,14,Fconfusing to someone with no prior
OL,15,Fknowledge. Either the channel is ITV 1
OL,16,For UTV.
OL,18,FThe obvious thing to do is to change
OL,19,Fthe EPG name to "ITV 1 UTV"
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
