OL,5,FNeither of these two changes would
OL,6,Fcause the sky to fall in but it would
OL,7,Fmake the channel name definitive.
OL,9,FThe UTV name appears to have a future
OL,10,Fas a trusted sub-brand under the ITV 1
OL,11,Fmasterbrand. A hallmark on local
OL,12,Foutput.
OL,14,FI would be surprised if UTV Live does
OL,15,Fnot adopt explicit ITV News branding at
OL,16,Fsome point but I would also be shocked
OL,17,Fif the name changed unless there was a
OL,18,Fwider shake-up across the network. It's
OL,19,Fno "worse" than ITV News Granada
OL,20,FReports or ITV News Meridian.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
